Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的推断很严谨\N{\fs38}There's no escaping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.82,0:00:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题出在\N{\fs38}The problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身上\N{\fs38}Is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fs38}and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我该离开的时候了 永别了\N{\fs38}I have to leave you... Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Michael 不可能是你的错\N{\fs38}Michael, you can't be the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我的错\N{\fs38}Oh, but I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道 建筑师是不允许住在\N{\fs38}You see, architects aren't supposed to live
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己设计的社区里的\N{\fs38}In the neighborhoods they design,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我太爱人类了 所以 我想试一试\N{\fs38}But I love humans, so I-I wanted to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我明白这是个错误了\N{\fs38}I see now that was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的掺和才是社区所有的灾难里\N{\fs38}My meddling is the one true constant
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一没变的因素\N{\fs38}In all of our disasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想强迫着Jianyu打开心扉\N{\fs38}I tried to force Jianyu into opening up,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果打开了一个地洞\N{\fs38}Which caused a sinkhole to open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把只小狗狗踢到了太阳上去\N{\fs38}I kicked a puppy into the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天就下起了垃圾雨\N{\fs38}And garbage rained down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全低估了迎新晚宴上\N{\fs38}I grossly underestimated the number of shrimp needed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要供应的虾的数量\N{\fs38}For the opening-night party,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天就飞得漫天都是\N{\fs38}And what flew through the sky the next day,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了嘲讽我失败了吗\N{\fs38}Taunting me for my failures?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起大家 真的很对不起\N{\fs38}I'm sorry, everyone. I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:00:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet\N{\fs38}Janet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我叫辆火车送我退休吧\N{\fs38}Please call a train to escort me into retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你们讲 出入社区唯一的途径\N{\fs38}You see, the only way in and out of a neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是坐火车\N{\fs38}Is by train,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet是唯一可以操纵火车的人\N{\fs38}And Janet is the only one who can operate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.95,0:01:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的Janet\N{\fs38}Oh, my dear Janet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.28,0:01:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走掉的话你没关系吧\N{\fs38}Will you be okay after I leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事儿\N{\fs38}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不会对我有任何影响\N{\fs38}This will not affect me in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 能不能有点同情心\N{\fs38}Jeez, show some compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我无法感到悲伤\N{\fs38}Well, I can't feel sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到最接近人类哭的事情就是\N{\fs38}But here's my best approximation of human crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔啊哇哇哇哇哇哇哇哇哇哇哇哇\N{\fs38}Baaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Janet 我真是太感动了  - 那就好\N{\fs38}- Oh, Janet, that was beautiful. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都跟他说了些啥\N{\fs38}What did you say to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你叫他这么做的吗\N{\fs38}Did you make him do this somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 这完全是他自己的主意\N{\fs38}Nope, this was entirely his idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老兄 这是个好消息啊\N{\fs38}Dude, this is good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Michael会安安然然地退休\N{\fs38}Michael's gonna get a chill retirement,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说 他也该安然一会儿了\N{\fs38}Which, frankly, he desperately needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我终于可以松口气\N{\fs38}And I can finally relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叉的太完美了\N{\fs38}It's forking perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这糟透了 Michael搞错了\N{\fs38}No, it's terrible. Michael's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错不在他\N{\fs38}He's not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但的确是他把我带来这的啊\N{\fs38}Well, Michael did bring me here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个错误才导致了后面这些岔子\N{\fs38}Which was the mistake that led to all the other problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这么说来 的确错就在他\N{\fs38}So, in that sense, he is the real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 这推理你怎么看 大伦理学家\N{\fs38}Ha! How do you like them ethics?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甩了你一脸伦理呢 Chidi\N{\fs38}I just ethics'd you in the face, Chidi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也没有改变我们在撒谎的事实\N{\fs38}It doesn't change the fact that we weren't truthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中国有句古老的谚语\N{\fs38}There's an old Chinese proverb--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"谎言呀像老虎\N{\fs38}"Lies are like tigers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶起来猛着呢"\N{\fs38}They are bad."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 就没了  - 用汉语讲起来更诗意的\N{\fs38}- That's it? - It's more poetic in mandarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Michael是要退休\N{\fs38}Look, Michael is retiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会乘条天使般的小船\N{\fs38}He's gonna be on an angel boat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去抽月光做的雪茄呢\N{\fs38}Somewhere smoking moonbeam cigars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tahani要给他办个欢送派对\N{\fs38}Now, Tahani is throwing him a good-bye party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去搭把手吧\N{\fs38}Let's go help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 这样我们就能弥补\N{\fs38}Sure, that will more than make up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带给他的伤害痛苦和谎言了\N{\fs38}For the pain and misery and lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 你总算开窍了\N{\fs38}Yes, now you're getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 Chidi 刚刚读完你的关于\N{\fs38}Hey, Chidi, just read your article
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逻辑实证主义的论文 太 枯燥了\N{\fs38}On logical positivism-- so dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 谢谢了 Henry\N{\fs38}Oh, thanks, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新靴子呀\N{\fs38}Whoa! New boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的 刚买的\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah, just got 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在商店第一眼看到 我就惊得\N{\fs38}Saw them in the store, and I was just like,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"哇喔噢"\N{\fs38}"Whoa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我说实话 你喜欢吗\N{\fs38}Tell the truth-- do you like 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs38}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 啊 喜欢  - 没有太红了吗\N{\fs38}- Oh, yeah. - Not too red?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没有  - 水钻没有太多吗\N{\fs38}- No. - Crystals aren't too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水钻一点也不多\N{\fs38}Crystals are not too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你这么说我就放心多了\N{\fs38}Oh, well, that makes me feel much better
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一直拿不定主意\N{\fs38}because I was really going back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道这靴子到底值不值这价钱\N{\fs38}Over whether they were worth the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这双靴子超级贵的\N{\fs38}They were super expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 看起来 超赞\N{\fs38}Yeah, well, they're, uh, amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我这辈子见过最赞的靴子了\N{\fs38}Those are the coolest boots I've ever seen in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢夸奖 哥们\N{\fs38}Thanks so much, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 拜\N{\fs38}Right. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天呐\N{\fs38}My god...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都做了些什么啊\N{\fs38}What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我们要完美地将 欢庆与敬佩\N{\fs38}Tonight needs to be the perfect blend of celebratory, reverential
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦辣酸甜 欢欣鼓舞 和 轻松自在 融合起来\N{\fs38}Bittersweet, upbeat, fun, and effortless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这将是 话题 "Tahani的美好时光"\N{\fs38}This is #tahanitime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在干嘛\N{\fs38}What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不行 Michael\N{\fs38}Oh, no, Michael,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不该来这看的 还没布置好呢\N{\fs38}You're not supposed to see it till it's all set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然来了 欢迎来到你的退休派对\N{\fs38}But, well, welcome to your retirement party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧那边 我布置好了餐台\N{\fs38}Look, over there, I've even set up a buffet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是主题甜品 像退休薄荷巧克力蛋糕 \N{\fs38}Of themed desserts, like retire-mint chocolate cake
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:03:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 "远行馅饼 "\N{\fs38}Or, uh, "Flan voyage."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 天呐\N{\fs38}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边还布置了一个皮纳塔\N{\fs38}Oh, and here we have a pinata
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照着你做的 和你一样有意思\N{\fs38}Shaped like you, which is always fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要问一下 你最喜欢什么颜色\N{\fs38}By the way, uh, what's your favorite color
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好来挑桌布\N{\fs38}For the tablecloths?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是种人类眼睛无法感悟的颜色\N{\fs38}Well, it's not perceptible by human eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做"胸膛荣光"\N{\fs38}It's called "Pleurigloss."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能描述一下吗\N{\fs38}Could you describe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是\N{\fs38}It's the color of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个士兵刚从战场下来回到家\N{\fs38}When a soldier comes home from war
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一眼看到自己狗狗的那种颜色\N{\fs38}And sees his dog for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不如就蓝色吧\N{\fs38}Hmm. How about blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tahani 很抱歉\N{\fs38}Tahani, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得马上取消这个派对\N{\fs38}We need to cancel this party immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊\N{\fs38}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我这样的人\N{\fs38}For a being like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退休\N{\fs38}Retirement...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是件好玩的事\N{\fs38}Is not something fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那"退休"对于你是什么样的\N{\fs38}What is "Retirement" for you exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来不想跟你们讲的 怕影响情绪\N{\fs38}Well, I wasn't gonna share this so as not to upset you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 其实是种\N{\fs38}But it's, a--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是种极端的惩罚形式\N{\fs38}An extreme form of punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们叫它"万年尖叫"\N{\fs38}We call it "The eternal shriek."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的灵魂会被打散\N{\fs38}My soul will be disintegrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一个分子都会散落异处\N{\fs38}And each molecule will be placed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在各个炽灼的太阳表面焚烧殆尽\N{\fs38}On the surface of a different burning sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会把我的 我的精髓从躯体中剜出\N{\fs38}And then my--my essence will be scooped out of my body
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用一把赤热的小勺浇在滚烫的钻石上\N{\fs38}With a flaming ladle and poured over hot diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钻石听起来蛮好的啊\N{\fs38}Oh, but the diamonds sound lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点儿也不好\N{\fs38}They're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身体余下的部分\N{\fs38}And then what's left of my body
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会永远地被一根钛合金棒子棍打\N{\fs38}Will be endlessly beaten with a titanium rod,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像\N{\fs38}Like a--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像个皮纳塔一样\N{\fs38}Like a pinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 只不过你们把吊绳系在我的腰上\N{\fs38}Yes, except you have the string around my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会把绳子系在我的生殖器上\N{\fs38}But instead it will definitely be around my genitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 天呐  - Michael 真的很抱歉\N{\fs38}- What? - Oh, Michael, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想要纪念你\N{\fs38}I was just trying to honor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你让我重新构思一下这个活动\N{\fs38}Please, allow me to reconceive the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fs38}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 大家伙儿 我们得从头开始\N{\fs38}All right, everyone, we're starting over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚的主题换成"阴郁"\N{\fs38}The key word for tonight is just "Somber."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jianyu 亲爱的 我们得把这些\N{\fs38}Jianyu, my love, we're gonna have to get rid of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派对小拉炮都处理掉 就现在\N{\fs38}all of the party poppers immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是拉掉他们\N{\fs38}No, not by using them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停 Jianyu 打住\N{\fs38}No, Jianyu. Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会受折磨\N{\fs38}He's gonna be tortured?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见鬼 我就差一点就完美地\N{\fs38}Dang it. I was almost handed a perfect solution
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不费一点功夫解决掉我所有的麻烦了\N{\fs38}To all my problems without having to work for it at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在都泡汤了\N{\fs38}And now it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么坏事总是落到平平凡凡的人头上\N{\fs38}Why do bad things always happen to mediocre people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是为保身份撒个小谎啊\N{\fs38}Who are lying about their identities?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有两个选择\N{\fs38}Okay, you have two options.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以坦白真相救Michael一把\N{\fs38}You can confess and save Michael,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者你可以继续撒谎\N{\fs38}Or you can continue to lie
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,置Michael于万劫不复的痛苦之中\N{\fs38}And condemn him to an eternity of unimaginable pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者 第三个选项\N{\fs38}Or option c--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒我自己的谎\N{\fs38}Continue to lie about myself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后找个法子救救Michael\N{\fs38}And find a way to save Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么方法能把Tahani推进火坑的吗\N{\fs38}Can we somehow throw Tahani under the bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就会是典型的\N{\fs38}That would be a classic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"一石二鸟"情况了\N{\fs38}"Two birds with one stone" Scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我还可以住进她的房子\N{\fs38}Plus, I'd get her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一石三鸟\N{\fs38}three birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 除了坦白没有别的方法了\N{\fs38}No, there's no way to stop this except confessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在随时随刻 Michael都有可能上火车\N{\fs38}Any moment now, Michael is going to get on that train,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就再也见不到他了\N{\fs38}And we will never see him again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像Lindeman教授\N{\fs38}Just like professor Lindeman
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请他再读一遍我3600页的手稿之后\N{\fs38}After I asked him to reread my 3,600-page manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他抽光了所有的烟\N{\fs38}He said he was going out for cigarettes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后辞掉了巴黎索邦学院的终身教职离开了\N{\fs38}But then he just left his tenured position at the Sorbonne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好一段故事 Janet\N{\fs38}Great story. Janet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈喽\N{\fs38}hi, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 唯一的\N{\fs38}Hi. So the only way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开社区的方法就是火车对吧\N{\fs38}Out of the neighborhood is a train?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我是唯一一个\N{\fs38}That's correct. I am the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能召唤火车的人 得要我才能操纵它\N{\fs38}Who can call the train, and it needs me to operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有个问题 可能会有点儿奇怪\N{\fs38}One more question, and, um, this is a little weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们能\N{\fs38}But can we...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关掉你吗\N{\fs38}Uh, shut you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能 好问题\N{\fs38}Yes, great question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个自毁开关\N{\fs38}There is a kill switch
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在社区里一个偏僻的地方\N{\fs38}In a remote sector of the neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我出了故障\N{\fs38}In the event that I malfunction
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者企图伤害这里的居民\N{\fs38}And attempt to harm the residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你按下开关 我将被摧毁\N{\fs38}If you press it, I will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 还有别的问题吗  - 没了 很好 谢谢\N{\fs38}- Anything else? - No, that's good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 哇哦 你想杀了Janet\N{\fs38}- Okay. - Whoa, you want to kill Janet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果Michael不离开的话他就没法退休\N{\fs38}Michael can't retire if he can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且他也走不了 如果没有Janet\N{\fs38}He can't leave if there's no Janet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火车的话\N{\fs38}To run the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个完美的解决方案\N{\fs38}It's a perfect solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet 击个掌怎么样\N{\fs38}Janet, high five, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 亲爱的\N{\fs38}Thanks, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不能杀了Janet\N{\fs38}You cannot kill Janet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人可是众所周知\N{\fs38}Killing is one of the most famous
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最不道德的禁止事项之一\N{\fs38}Moral no-nos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet是被送到这儿帮助我们的非人类存在体\N{\fs38}Janet is a nonhuman object who was sent here to help us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而她帮我们的方法就是让我们杀了她\N{\fs38}And the way she can help us is if we kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做的只是稍带点谋杀意味的事\N{\fs38}We're doing one small murder-y thing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出于一个更远大 更好的理由\N{\fs38}For a bigger, better reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要目的正当 可以不择手段\N{\fs38}The ends justify the means.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这话是谁说的吗\N{\fs38}Do you know who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是某个美好又善良的人 就像Oprah\N{\fs38}Was it someone nice and great, like Oprah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}Oprah：美国电视节目主持人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Machiavelli说的\N{\fs38}It was Machiavelli...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}Machiavelli：马基雅弗利，意大利新兴资产阶级思想政治家、历史学家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个跟Oprah一点边不沾的人\N{\fs38}a very non-Oprah-like figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们杀了她之后会怎样\N{\fs38}And what happens after we kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不得不就我们做的事向每个人撒谎\N{\fs38}We'll have to lie to everyone about what we did,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒谎始终是错的\N{\fs38}And lying is always wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么我要告诉Henry我喜欢他的靴子\N{\fs38}Why? Why would I tell Henry that I liked his boots?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢 我讨厌他的靴子\N{\fs38}I don't like his boots. I hate his boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我知道\N{\fs38}Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两天前你就跟我说过了\N{\fs38}You've talked about it for the last two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对他撒谎了 你写的论文是关于康德的\N{\fs38}I lied to him. You wrote your thesis on Kant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康德认为撒谎在道德上始终是错的\N{\fs38}He believed that lying is always morally wrong--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有例外\N{\fs38}No exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 康德是个孤独且痴迷于宗教的隐士\N{\fs38}Yes, well, Kant was a lonely, obsessive hermit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一个朋友也没有\N{\fs38}With zero friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时我们做事只是出于礼貌\N{\fs38}Sometimes we do thing just to be polite,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你真的对这件事耿耿于怀\N{\fs38}But if you really feel that strongly about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就告诉他真相\N{\fs38}Tell him the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我也不在乎\N{\fs38}Also, I don't care,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为现在已经是午夜了\N{\fs38}'cause it's the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是为什么人人都讨厌伦理学家\N{\fs38}This is why everyone hates moral philosophy professors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗\N{\fs38}They do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Chidi\N{\fs38}Hey, Chidi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你今天来听我的课了  - 嗯 是的 没错\N{\fs38}- You sit in on my class today? - Uh, I did, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒的课 顺便说一句—非常出色\N{\fs38}Great lecture, by the way-- so bleak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 伙计\N{\fs38}Thanks, bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来听课真是太完美了\N{\fs38}It's actually perfect that you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有东西给你\N{\fs38}I got something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 老天\N{\fs38}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很喜欢我的那双\N{\fs38}You loved mine so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我决定给你一双属于你自己的\N{\fs38}I decided to get you your own pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以当靴子兄弟了\N{\fs38}We can be boot brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 这个我不能收 这靴子太贵了\N{\fs38}Wow. I can't accept these. They're too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当然可以收下 快试试 朋友\N{\fs38}Sure you can. Try 'em on, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么喜欢我的靴子\N{\fs38}The fact that you liked mine so much
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我觉得买下他们是个正确的决定\N{\fs38}Really made me feel like I made the right choice to buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟 不该只有我享受乐趣和好靴子 对吧\N{\fs38}After all, why should I have all the fun and boots, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我不 我不知道\N{\fs38}I-I don't--I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来棒极了\N{\fs38}Those look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿着它们转一圈\N{\fs38}Take 'em for a spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你简直帅的飞起\N{\fs38}you're flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢\N{\fs38}Mm, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发表演讲了 演讲时间到了 各位\N{\fs38}Speeches! Time for speeches, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Michael 作为一个并没有真正\N{\fs38}Michael, as someone who didn't exactly have
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受过完整父母教导的人\N{\fs38}The steadiest parental guidance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想谢谢您\N{\fs38}I just want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是在那儿守护着我们\N{\fs38}You were always there for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本不该那样的 我是个麻烦\N{\fs38}I shouldn't have been. I was the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 但\N{\fs38}Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不在的时候一切也都很好\N{\fs38}It was also great when you weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 很快我就不在了 永远不在\N{\fs38}Don't worry. Soon I won't be...Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那万年尖叫\N{\fs38}Because of the eternal shriek!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 谢谢你 Glenn\N{\fs38}Yes, thank you, Glenn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说的是\N{\fs38}Look, what I'm trying to say is this--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Michael 你总是给我们温暖还有安全感\N{\fs38}Michael, you always kept us warm and safe
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像那明亮而炙热的太阳\N{\fs38}Like a bright, glowing sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我踢了只狗上去那个\N{\fs38}Like the one I kicked the dog into
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是我将在其美好温暖的表面\N{\fs38}Or the one I'm going to be burned
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被烧焦的那个\N{\fs38}On the surface of fraternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 没有别的发言了\N{\fs38}Okay, no more speeches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演讲结束\N{\fs38}Speeches are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在Michael准备讲话了\N{\fs38}Michael's going to talk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我很抱歉我之前脾气太暴躁\N{\fs38}Ugh, I'm sorry I was so grumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是因为必须要离开而有点难过\N{\fs38}It's just I'm sad that I have to leave
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没做完那些\N{\fs38}Before doing all the human things
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做的人类的事\N{\fs38}That I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把头发弄湿\N{\fs38}I wanted to get my hair wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗 我 我想试着拉伤一下腿筋\N{\fs38}You know, I-I wanted to pull a hamstring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞清楚"向着"和"朝着"的区别\N{\fs38}To learn the difference between "Toward" And "Towards."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想试试当你沿着过道走的时候\N{\fs38}I wanted to do that thing where you walk down the hallway,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎面走来另一个人\N{\fs38}And someone else is walking the other way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都靠向同一边\N{\fs38}And then you both lean to one side
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后又同时靠向另一边\N{\fs38}And then the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你们为这种共同的小失误暗暗发笑\N{\fs38}And then you both chuckle over your shared foible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要一张优惠卡\N{\fs38}I wanted to get a rewards card,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么优惠卡都行\N{\fs38}Any rewards card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我想跟人简单谈谈然后说\N{\fs38}I-I wanted to talk briefly to someone and then say,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"污一点儿没事"\N{\fs38}"Take it sleazy."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃一块苏打饼干\N{\fs38}I wanted to eat a saltine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 其实我有一些苏打饼干\N{\fs38}Oh! I actually have some saltines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 尝尝\N{\fs38}Here, try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太干了\N{\fs38}Pretty dry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且太咸\N{\fs38}And too salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 低调地从这儿出去吧\N{\fs38}Well, going out on a real low note here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 再见 各位\N{\fs38}Okay, bye, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 污一点儿没事\N{\fs38}Well, take it sleazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说了那句话\N{\fs38}You got to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 然后你就可以回我一句\N{\fs38}Yes, but then you say it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这一点儿不自然\N{\fs38}No, it's not organic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 Janet 这儿有过多少个"Janet"\N{\fs38}Uh, Janet, how many "Janets" Have there been?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共二十五代"Janet"\N{\fs38}There have been 25 generations of janet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个升级版的Janet都会更有智慧\N{\fs38}Each new update of Janet gains more wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有更强的社会能力\N{\fs38}And social abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的是 第一代Janet有个点击式触摸转盘\N{\fs38}Fun fact--the first janet had a click wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那它跟人一样会变老吗\N{\fs38}So it's like aging for a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你会长大吗\N{\fs38}You're--you're growing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很想那样 Chidi\N{\fs38}That's how I like to think of it, chidi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能吃东西 所以每次有新版的Janet诞生\N{\fs38}I can't eat, so every time there's a new version of janet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢拿一块生日蛋糕\N{\fs38}I like to take a piece of birthday cake
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝我嘴的部位拍上去\N{\fs38}And smash it around where my mouth is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 Janet已经 已经会学习和成长了\N{\fs38}Look, janet has-- has learned and grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有真正的生活 我们不能杀了她\N{\fs38}She's essentially living a life. We can't kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样的态度 我们当然不能\N{\fs38}Not with that attitude, we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 伙计 我死了 你也死了\N{\fs38}Listen, man, I'm dead, you're dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都死了 现在我们再杀了她\N{\fs38}We all died, and now we're killing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续传承下去\N{\fs38}Pay it forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不 这句话不是这么说的\N{\fs38}Uh, no, that's not what that means at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eleanor\N{\fs38} Eleanor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在这儿\N{\fs38}Here we are .
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要按下那个按钮 然后就永别了 Janet\N{\fs38}Just press that button, and it's good-bye, janet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chidi 我看得出你在担心\N{\fs38}Chidi, I can see that you're worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想向你保证\N{\fs38}And I just want to assure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是人类 我也感觉不到痛\N{\fs38}I am not human, and I cannot feel pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 谢谢 这起了点作用\N{\fs38}Ah, thank you. That helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我必须警告你\N{\fs38}However, I should warn you--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的程序里带有一套自动防故障措施\N{\fs38}I am programmed with a fail-safe measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你靠近自毁开关时\N{\fs38}As you approach the kill switch,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会求你饶命\N{\fs38}I will begin to beg for my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是为防止意外停机而设置的\N{\fs38}It's just there in case of an accidental shut down,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但会看起来很逼真\N{\fs38}But it will seem very real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷 所以谁来做这个 我还是你\N{\fs38}Cool. So who's doing this, me or you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我来吧\N{\fs38}I think I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不知为什么 当个旁观者看起来更糟 \N{\fs38}Um, being a bystander seems worse, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 开始吧\N{\fs38}Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chidi 不 不 不 Chidi 求你了\N{\fs38}Chidi, no, no, no! Chidi, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你 求求你 求你不要伤害我\N{\fs38}Please, please, please don't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想死 拜托 拜托了\N{\fs38}I don't want to die! Please, please--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs38}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说一次 我不是人类\N{\fs38}Again, I am not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会死的\N{\fs38}I can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是被人格化的盛装知识的容器\N{\fs38}I am simply an anthropomorphized vessel of knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为便利你的生活而被制造的\N{\fs38}Built to make your life easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的求饶看起来太真实了\N{\fs38}You're pleading seems so real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 是的 这是个很有用的自动防故障措施\N{\fs38}Oh, yes, it is a very effective fail-safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是我想杀机器人的 对吗\N{\fs38}Ugh, you want a robot killed right,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以得自己动手\N{\fs38}You have to do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eleanor Eleanor 不 不 不\N{\fs38}Eleanor? Eleanor, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 等等 等等 等等 等等 Eleanor 我还有孩子\N{\fs38}Please, wait, wait, wait, wait. Eleanor, I have kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有三个漂亮的孩子\N{\fs38}I have three beautiful children--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tyler Emma还有小宝贝Phillip\N{\fs38}Tyler, Emma, and little, tiny baby Phillip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看Tyler\N{\fs38}Look at Tyler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有哮喘 但他像个冠军一样跟病魔战斗\N{\fs38}Tyler has asthma, but he is battling it like a champ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看他 不 Eleanor 看着他\N{\fs38}Look at him. No, Eleanor, look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着他们\N{\fs38}Look at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着他们\N{\fs38}look at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这太逼真了\N{\fs38}Aah! It's so realistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eleanor 再说一次 我不是人类\N{\fs38}Eleanor, again, I'm not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是张素材照片\N{\fs38}This is a stock photo of the crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼克儿童频道"孩子的选择"奖上的照片\N{\fs38}At the Nickelodeon kids' choice awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这不是真的\N{\fs38}that's right, it's not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们搞定它 好的\N{\fs38}Let's just do this. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 我还有很多事要做\N{\fs38}Please, I have so much to live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不 不 不 求你了  - 我们还没靠近那儿\N{\fs38}- No, no, no, please. - We're not even near the--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计们 怎么了\N{\fs38}Hey, guys, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个聚会太差劲了 所以我溜了\N{\fs38}That party was lame, so I bailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我看到你们 跟着你们来到这儿\N{\fs38}Then I saw you, so I followed you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 瞧 一个按钮 不 不 不\N{\fs38}Oh, look, a button. No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jianyu 不\N{\fs38}Jianyu, no!
