Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么怎么办\N{\fs38}What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chidi 你刚杀死了Janet\N{\fs38}Chidi, you just murdered Janet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得赶紧离开犯罪现场\N{\fs38}We have to flee your crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑啊\N{\fs38}Run!
