Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"请注意 我被"\N{\fs38}"Attention--I have--"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"请注意 我被杀害了"\N{\fs38}"Attention-- I have been murdered."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 兄弟 速成教学 做了坏事不被逮着\N{\fs38}Okay, dude, crash course in getting away with bad stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得表现的镇定跟没事儿一样\N{\fs38}You have to act calm and cool
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你跟这世界一毛钱关系都没有\N{\fs38}like you don't have a care in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗\N{\fs38}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs38}Great.
