Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像电影里戴了副太阳镜的死人\N{\fs38}'cause you're a dead guy in sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看多好玩儿啊 是不是 Chidi\N{\fs38}We have fun, don't we, Chidi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这一辈子从来没有这么大压力过\N{\fs38}I've never been more stressed out in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你需要点儿啥\N{\fs38}I know what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet 你能给Chidi搞点大麻来吗\N{\fs38}Janet, can you get Chidi some weed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 对了 你弄死了Janet\N{\fs38}Oh, that's right. You killed Janet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet被人杀害了\N{\fs38}Well, Janet's been murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是给这个好日子又带来一个亮点\N{\fs38}That's a nice capper to this wonderful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在还不清楚这是怎么回事\N{\fs38}I don't really know what happens now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为Janet从未被人杀害过\N{\fs38}because Janet has never been murdered before--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是今天 在我眼皮子底下\N{\fs38}Only today, here on my watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:33.07,goodbye,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz351.9\frx6\fry4\pos(385.143,112.286)}{\fn方正大黑_GBK}{\c&H5D565E&}走好 Janet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:33.07,goodbye,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\frz354.3\frx8\fry12\pos(395.429,187.714)}{\fn方正大黑_GBK}{\c&H5D565E&}安息吧 我们逝去的姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是被派对分散了注意力\N{\fs38}while I was distracted with a party that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个派对是Tahani为我张罗的\N{\fs38}Tahani was throwing for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而我并不想要\N{\fs38}which I didn't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Michael 你可千万别怪自己啊\N{\fs38}Michael, you mustn't blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有 我在怪你\N{\fs38}I'm not. I'm blaming you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 关于Janet还有什么可说的呢\N{\fs38}Anyway, what is there to say about Janet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有哪些没被警报说到的呢\N{\fs38}that hasn't already been said by the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是天空上巨大的Janet警报\N{\fs38}giant Janet alarm in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我被人杀害了"\N{\fs38}"I've been murdered"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这道出了一切\N{\fs38}I think that says it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好呀\N{\fs38}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet \N{\fs38}Janet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你复活啦\N{\fs38}you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 建筑师\N{\fs38}Hello, architect,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请输入你的四位数密码\N{\fs38}Please enter your four-digit pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 是啥来着 呃 是啥来着\N{\fs38}Uh, what is it? Uh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥来着 哦 对了 对了\N{\fs38}What is it? Um--oh, right, right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 呃 我的出生年份\N{\fs38}It's my, uh--my birth year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs38}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得换个密码 这个太好猜了\N{\fs38}I got to change that. That's too easy to guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet\N{\fs38}Janet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁杀害了你\N{\fs38}Who murdered you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 噢 不  - 嘘 没事的\N{\fs38}- Oh. Oh, no. - Shh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 嗯 你好\N{\fs38}- Hello. - Yes, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs38}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 呃\N{\fs38}Yeah. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是她的记忆被清除了\N{\fs38}Her memory must have been wiped clean,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在要重新上传\N{\fs38}So now she's gonna have to re-upload
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙中的所有知识\N{\fs38}all the knowledge in the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这得花好几天时间 好吧\N{\fs38}which will only take a few days. Okay--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 你好\N{\fs38}- Hello. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs38}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好呀\N{\fs38}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 在我搞清楚这件事之前\N{\fs38}Everyone, um, until I get to the bottom of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的退休被正式推迟\N{\fs38}my retirement is officially postponed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fs38}Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 你好\N{\fs38}Hello. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得承认 我算是搞定了\N{\fs38}You got to admit-- I kind of nailed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在要做的 就是永远保守秘密\N{\fs38}All we have to do now is keep the secret forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伙伴J 你能行吗\N{\fs38}J-dog, you cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不好 等我到了皮纳塔那儿\N{\fs38}No, by the time I got to the piñata,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的糖都没了\N{\fs38}All the candy was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会告诉任何人的\N{\fs38}He's not gonna tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chidi 我的小Chidi\N{\fs38}Chidi? Cheedster?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦\N{\fs38}What's, uh, happening, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼神很奇怪\N{\fs38}You have a crazy look in your eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在往自己衬衫里缩\N{\fs38}And you're retreating into your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得像缩头乌龟一样\N{\fs38}You're kind of turtling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Henry 你没事吧 怎么啦\N{\fs38}Henry, are you all right? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我长了个动脉瘤\N{\fs38}I have an aneurysm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做紧急手术\N{\fs38}Requires emergency surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生说我的存活率只有50%\N{\fs38}Doctor's give me a 50/50 chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 如果你想跟我说什么的话\N{\fs38}So, if there's anything you need to say to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在就得说了\N{\fs38}You should do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs38}Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实吧\N{\fs38}Actually, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里允许穿靴子呢\N{\fs38}They let you wear your boots in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是唯一给我带来安慰的东西\N{\fs38}They're the only things that bring me comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才想跟我说什么\N{\fs38}What did you want to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 呃\N{\fs38}Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想说 有我在\N{\fs38}Just that I'm here and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你 兄弟\N{\fs38}I love you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\fs38}I love you, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靴子兄弟\N{\fs38}boot brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘛\N{\fs38}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.79,医院,,0,0,0,,{\c&H8A797B&\frz350.7\frx18\fry30\pos(362.285,212.858)}{\fn张海山锐谐体}{\fs30}悉尼综合医院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chidi\N{\fs38}Chidi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用在这待一整晚的\N{\fs38}You didn't have to stay here all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手术顺利吗 切除干净了\N{\fs38}So surgery went well? All clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常顺利\N{\fs38}Right as rain, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:18:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太 太 太好了\N{\fs38}That is so, so, so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我讨厌你的靴子  - 啥\N{\fs38}- I hate your boots. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年前我告诉你我特喜欢你的靴子\N{\fs38}I told you that I loved your boots three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时在撒谎\N{\fs38}and I was lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时起这个谎就一直跟着我\N{\fs38}and that lie has haunted me ever since,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人一直告诉我没关系的\N{\fs38}and people tried to tell me it was fine--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说这只是善意的白色谎言 是社交礼节\N{\fs38}just a nice, little white lie in the form of social niceties--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不这么想 然后昨天\N{\fs38}But I disagreed, and then yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你要走了 但现在你还活着\N{\fs38}I thought you were gonna die, but now you're not dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于可以诚实一回\N{\fs38}and I can finally be honest
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你这双靴子很丑很糟糕\N{\fs38}and say that those boots are terrible and hideous
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌它\N{\fs38}and I hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼\N{\fs38}Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是为啥人人都讨厌伦理学教授\N{\fs38}This is why everyone hates moral philosophy professors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道\N{\fs38}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也明白\N{\fs38}And I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管她复活了\N{\fs38}I don't care that she came back
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者我们是出于好意\N{\fs38}or that we did it for a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了活在谎言中\N{\fs38}I can't live with this lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去自首 承认自己杀了Janet\N{\fs38}I'm going to confess to the murder of Janet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老兄 为啥想不开\N{\fs38}Dude, Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet好得很\N{\fs38}Janet is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没伤到她一根汗毛\N{\fs38}We didn't harm her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有么\N{\fs38}We didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Janet\N{\fs38}Hey, Janet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs38}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 你好\N{\fs38}- Hello. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet 麻烦你背一下英文字母表好吗\N{\fs38}Janet, would you please recite the English alphabet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A B\N{\fs38}A-B...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet\N{\fs38}Janet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她知道A B Janet\N{\fs38}She knows her a-b-Janets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是真的知道宇宙中的一切知识\N{\fs38}She literally knew everything in the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在却变成了婴儿\N{\fs38}and now she's a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算她没事\N{\fs38}And even if she were okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说骗人太痛苦\N{\fs38}it would be too painful for me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了一直骗人\N{\fs38}to live with these lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在胡说八道什么呢\N{\fs38}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒谎骗人相当简单啊\N{\fs38}It is so easy to live with a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次我假装自己有绝症\N{\fs38}I once pretended to have a terminal illness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在太阳眼镜店里见到了Scott Wolf\N{\fs38}to meet Scott Wolf at a Sunglass Hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}Scott Wolf 美国演员 出演美剧<夜班医生><罪案第六感><五口之家>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有受害者的罪行\N{\fs38}Victimless crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吧\N{\fs38}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会说出去 因为我答应了要帮你\N{\fs38}I won't say anything because I promised to help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于我们的所作所为\N{\fs38}and the moral implications of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折射出的道德内涵 实在太错综复杂\N{\fs38}everything that we've done are so complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能永远都理不清楚 但我还是讨厌撒谎\N{\fs38}that I may never untangle them, but I hate lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都讨厌\N{\fs38}I always have,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事会把我生吞活剥的\N{\fs38}and this is going to eat me up inside forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到不屑一顾 忘了就算\N{\fs38}You might be able to shrug this off and forget about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我永远不能\N{\fs38} but I never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs38}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs38}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs38}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs38}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs38}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jianyu\N{\fs38}Jianyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Michael Janet说你想找我聊聊\N{\fs38}Michael, Janet said you wanted to speak to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:19:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实她只是一直在流口水\N{\fs38}Well, actually, she was just drooling a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不停地说"你好"\N{\fs38}and saying "Hello"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了一遍又一遍\N{\fs38}over and over again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她确实往你这边指\N{\fs38}but she did point at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我欠你一个道歉\N{\fs38}I owe you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 别 不需要的\N{\fs38}Oh, no. No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你请继续\N{\fs38}But please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是想帮忙\N{\fs38}You were only trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一个特别好的人\N{\fs38}You're a wonderful person,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我还有机会开退休派对\N{\fs38}And if I ever do have a retirement party,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望是你来策划\N{\fs38}I hope you plan it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好 谢谢你们过来\N{\fs38}Thank you for gathering, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想给大家汇报一下新进展\N{\fs38}I want to keep you all updated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我目前所知\N{\fs38}Here's what we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人杀死了Janet\N{\fs38}Someone slaughtered Janet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\fs38}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 天哪  - 没事的\N{\fs38}- Oh, boy. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜测这个可怕的事件\N{\fs38}I assume that this horrifying act
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少都与这里之前发生的事情有关联\N{\fs38}is somehow related to the other issues we've had here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也意味着\N{\fs38}It also means
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个社区里出现的问题\N{\fs38}that the problems in this neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非百分百是我的责任\N{\fs38}are not 100% my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一些什么别的东西在搞事\N{\fs38}There is something else at work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果关于此事\N{\fs38}If anyone has any information
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人有任何消息\N{\fs38}about any of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请求你\N{\fs38}I beg you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我\N{\fs38}tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 我爱你\N{\fs38}Hey, I love you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Michael\N{\fs38}Michael...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社区里的大麻烦\N{\fs38}The problem in the neighborhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fs38}is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是误入善地的\N{\fs38}I was brought to the good place by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本不应该来这里\N{\fs38}I'm not supposed to be here.
